<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
<p style="color: #e45206; font-size: 35px; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">Let&rsquo;s Talk!</p>
<p style="color: #1c3f94; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">Now you can see why I&rsquo;m so excited to show you how a Sungage loan can be applied to your home&rsquo;s solar project. So what&rsquo;s stopping you? Contact me today to set up your appointment.</p>
<p style="color: #61af3f; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;"><span class="appleLinksGreen"><a href="mailto:david.carpenter@directenergysolar.com" style="text-decoration: none; color: #61af3f;">David Carpenter</a></span></p>
<p style="color: #61af3f; font-size: 21px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;"><span class="appleLinksGreen"><a href="mailto:david.carpenter@directenergysolar.com" style="text-decoration: none; color: #61af3f;">david.carpenter@directenergysolar.com</a></span></p>
</div>
