<table width="700" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" ><tr ><td style="padding-top:20px; padding-bottom:33px; padding-left:33px; padding-right:33px; " ><div style="color:#666666; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:11px; line-height:16px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="disclaimerCopyWhy" ><p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;">You&rsquo;re receiving this email because you&rsquo;ve expressed interest in a Direct Energy Solar system installation.</p></div>
<div class="mktEditable" id="disclaimerCopyTerms" ><p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><sup>1</sup>Customers must meet certain criteria to qualify for financing, including without limitation a minimum FICO score of 640, with a maximum debt-to-income of 50%. The residence must be the homeowner&rsquo;s primary residence, not held in trust, and with no subdivided deed. Other restrictions apply. Rates are effective as of <span class="appleLinksGray">10/1/2015</span> and are subject to change.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><sup>&dagger;</sup> Financing applications are processed by Digital Federal Credit Union (DCU) and DCU is the creditor for any such approved financing.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><sup>2</sup>To qualify for Sungage SREC products, the project must have pre-paid data acquisition/reporting services. The Sungage SREC product cannot be bundled with loans other than the Sungage loan product. Customers do not need to use the SREC product to get a Sungage loan product. There are no fees for Sungage SREC products.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray">Offers and financing are available to customers who qualify, vary by location, and are not available in all areas. We customize our solar power system specifically for your home, therefore, pricing, savings, utility bill, solar bill amounts and actual returns vary based on different factors including but not limited to your location, system size, available solar incentives and local utility rates. See terms and conditions for more details.</span></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray">AZ ROC 292637, CA CSLB 992952, CT HIC 06289933/ELC 0200988, DE 2014104056/T1-0005731, DC 420212000078/ECC 902554, MA HIC 168228/ELC 21555A, MD ELC 12327/HIC 126447, NJ HIC 13VH05618900/ELC 34EB01175700, PA HIC PA023535, Suffolk 54817-H, Putnam PC66168, Rockland H-11532</span></p></div>
